          <div class="faq-answer">Thermo Fisher has highly recurring revenue streams and a wide moat in the life sciences tools industry. This lower risk profile, combined with a 4.18% risk-free rate, justifies an 8% required rate of return, typical for stable, defensive healthcare compounders.</div>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>Is this a buy recommendation?</summary>
